### 5. Invalid: Try to revert a published course back to draft
POST {{baseUrl}}/course/edit/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isDraft": true
}


### 6. Invalid: Try to set end date in the past
POST {{baseUrl}}/course/edit/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endDate": "2020-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
}


#==================================== FILTER ====================================

### 7. List Courses - Standard Retrieve (Active/Upcoming Courses)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?userId=6a1e80665979beee41cf5f4b&filter=organizer
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 8. List Courses - Filter by Status (Explicitly show Past courses)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?status=Past
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 9. List Courses - Multi-way Filtering (Custom date range + Category + Search + Status combined)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?fromDate=2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z&toDate=2026-12-31T23:59:59.000Z&categoryId=647f1234567890abcdef1234&search=Node&status=Upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 10. List Courses - Time Slot Presets (Happenings Soon, This Month, Today, This Weekend, etc.)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?filter=happeningsoon,thismonth
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 11. List Courses - Time of Day Slot Filter (Morning, Afternoon, Evening)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?timeOfDay=morning,afternoon
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 12. List Courses - Geospatial Distance Search (Radius of 100km from Lat/Lng coordinates)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?latitude=37.774929&longitude=-122.419416&radius=100
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 13. List Courses - Viewport Bounding Box Map Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?north=37.850000&south=37.700000&east=-122.350000&west=-122.480000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 14. List Courses - Organizer Courses (Latest Created First)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?page=1&limit=3&filter=organizer&status=Live,Upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 14.b. List Courses - Organizer Live and Upcoming Courses (Excludes Past Courses)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?filter=organizer,fixedstart&status=Live,Upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 14.a. List Courses - Sorted by Latest Created (Public exploration)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?filter=latest
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 15. List Courses - Organizer Courses Filtered by Ongoing Enrollment
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?filter=organizer,ongoing
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 16. List Courses - Organizer Courses Filtered by fixedStart Enrollment
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?filter=organizer,fixedstart
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 17. List Courses - Organizer Draft Courses Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?filter=organizer,draft
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 17.a List Courses - Exclude My Created Courses (using excludeMyCourses query parameter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?excludeMyCourses=true
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 17.b List Courses - Exclude My Created Courses (using excludemycourses filter keyword)
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/list?filter=excludemycourses
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 18. Retrieve Course Booking Cut-off Options
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/booking-cutoffs


#===========================ANALYTICS==============================================================

### 19. Organizer Courses Analytics Summary
# Retrieves analytics summary for all courses created by the organizer.
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/analytics/summary?filter=7d
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 20. Single Course Analytics Details
# Retrieves analytics detail for a single course.
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/analytics/{{courseId}}?filter=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


#=================================== CANCELLATION ===================================================

### 21. Cancel a Course
# Organizer or Admin cancels an entire course (with optional batchId and reason).
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/cancel-course
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}",
  "reason": "Cancelled due to unforeseen circumstances."
}

### 21b. Cancel a Specific Batch of a Course
# Organizer or Admin cancels a specific batch of a course (by providing batchId).
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/cancel-course
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}",
  "batchId": "6a216d3aaf039f44dc5d6ef9",
  "reason": "Cancelled this specific batch due to low enrollment."
}

### 21c. Cancel a Specific Slot/Date of a Batch
# Organizer cancels only a specific date for an ongoing batch
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/cancel-course
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}",
  "batchId": "6a27a6008db41086df1e5e06",
  "date": "2026-06-15",
  "reason": "Instructor unavailable for this day."
}



#=====================================COURSE DETAILS===================================================

### 22. Get Course Details
# Retrieves the details of a single course by its ID.
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/details/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


#==================================== ENROLLED USERS ==============================

### 23. Get Course Enrolled Users List (Attendees)
# Retrieves the list of users who enroller this course.
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/course/{{courseId}}/attendees
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 23b. Get Course Enrolled Users — Filtered by Batch
# Retrieves the list of users who enroller this course filtered by batch ID.
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/course/{{courseId}}/attendees?batchId=6a216d3aaf039f44dc5d6ef9
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 23c. Get Course Enrolled Users — Paginated, Search by Name or bookingId (single field)
# Retrieves the list of users who enroller this course filtered by name or booking ID in a single search parameter and paginated.
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/course/{{courseId}}/attendees?page=1&limit=5&search=&batchId=6a30da7e51595a97343397a6&date=2026-06-22
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 23d. Get Course Enrolled Users — Filtered by Date (Ongoing Classes)
# Retrieves the list of users who enroller this course filtered by ongoing class date or day.
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/course/{{courseId}}/attendees?date=2026-06-15
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


#==================================== RESERVATIONS ================================

### 24. Adjust Course Reserved Seats (Date-specific external reservations)
# Organizer adjusts ReservedExternally seats for a specific date slot of a batch.
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/adjust-course-reserved-seats
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}",
  "batchId": "6a30da7e51595a97343397a6",
  "date": "2026-06-22",
  "ReservedExternally": 3
}


#==================================== CANCELLATION ==================================

### 25. Cancel a Specific Batch (Only bookings in this batch get refunded)
# This sets batch.status → "Cancelled" but keeps the course active.
# Only transactions with this batchId are refunded.
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/cancel-course
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}",
  "batchId": "6a2904769f3feca6e22f5917",
  "reason": "Not enough enrollment for this batch"
}

### 26. Cancel Entire Course (Organizer — all bookings get full refund)
# This sets course.status → "Cancelled", cancels all batches, and refunds ALL bookings.
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/cancel-course
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}",
  "reason": "Instructor unavailable"
}

